<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 14:07:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“记住我们的名字”：由于害怕被遗忘，年轻的加沙人在临终前记录了最后的遗嘱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/remember-our-names-fearing-oblivion-young-gazans-recorded-last-wills-before-dying/00000191-4b2b-dfee-a3f3-5feb9a300000</link><description>一位从未离开家的足球运动员、一位想要提高政治意识的经济学家以及一位即使在死后仍继续提供内容的电影制片人。自战争开始以来，他们是加沙地带 4 万人遇难的人之一。除了死亡之外，许多人还担心自己会成为“一个数字”，并采取措施确保他们不会被遗忘</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 13:47:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/remember-our-names-fearing-oblivion-young-gazans-recorded-last-wills-before-dying/00000191-4b2b-dfee-a3f3-5feb9a300000</guid></item><item><title>由辛贝特和摩萨德领导人率领的以色列团队抵达多哈参加加沙停火峰会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/led-by-shin-bet-and-mossad-chiefs-israeli-team-heads-to-doha-for-gaza-cease-fire-summit/00000191-5231-d984-a5ff-f2f713580000</link><description>一名巴勒斯坦高级官员告诉《国土报》，内塔尼亚胡和某些内阁成员的言论表明谈判不太可能取得进展，其成功取决于美国的压力</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 12:29:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/led-by-shin-bet-and-mossad-chiefs-israeli-team-heads-to-doha-for-gaza-cease-fire-summit/00000191-5231-d984-a5ff-f2f713580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列航空公司在加沙战争的帮助下季度利润创纪录的 1.47 亿美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-airline-el-al-rakes-in-record-147m-in-quarterly-profits-with-help-of-gaza-war/00000191-552a-d5d7-adbb-757a65c80000</link><description>得益于在以色列运营的外国航空公司的竞争减少，该公司在本世纪初面临着严重的财务困境，但今年第二季度自 2022 年底以来的净财务债务减少了 10.89 亿美元</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 10:36:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-airline-el-al-rakes-in-record-147m-in-quarterly-profits-with-help-of-gaza-war/00000191-552a-d5d7-adbb-757a65c80000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯卫生部称，自战争开始以来，加沙死亡人数已超过4万</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/gaza-death-toll-surpasses-40-000-since-war-began-hamas-health-ministry-says/00000191-4c06-d695-a7b5-de0f450a0000</link><description>据哈马斯管理的卫生部称，约 70% 的伤亡者是妇女和儿童，约 17,000 名儿童失去了父母之一或双亲。 ■ 加沙的卫生系统处于崩溃边缘，约 12,000 名伤者需要紧急疏散接受治疗国外</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 10:08:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/gaza-death-toll-surpasses-40-000-since-war-began-hamas-health-ministry-says/00000191-4c06-d695-a7b5-de0f450a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡办公室要求甘茨偿还美国正式访问费用19,000美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-demands-gantz-pay-back-19-000-for-official-u-s-visit/00000191-54d4-d5d7-adbb-74f406340000</link><description>以色列议员本尼·甘茨（Benny Gantz）还是内塔尼亚胡战时内阁成员时进行的三月访问包括与副总统哈里斯和其他官员的会面。项目办称甘茨无权进行此次访问</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 07:40:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-demands-gantz-pay-back-19-000-for-official-u-s-visit/00000191-54d4-d5d7-adbb-74f406340000</guid></item><item><title>以色列掌握着释放人质的关键 - 但伊朗将决定中东是否爆发战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-holds-the-key-to-freeing-the-hostages-but-iran-decides-if-the-region-goes-to-war/00000191-52b5-dc60-a397-57f5b6310000</link><description>周四的多哈峰会就像一个俄罗斯娃娃，充满了层层障碍：目前还不清楚内塔尼亚胡给了以色列谈判代表多大的灵活性，以及​​这对哈马斯来说是否足够；没有人知道伊朗和真主党是否会以加沙停火为借口，放弃对两起耻辱性暗杀事件的军事反应</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 03:02:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-holds-the-key-to-freeing-the-hostages-but-iran-decides-if-the-region-goes-to-war/00000191-52b5-dc60-a397-57f5b6310000</guid></item><item><title>美国在加沙峰会前加大压力 - 并计划在失败后改变策略</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/u-s-steps-up-the-pressure-ahead-of-gaza-summit-and-plans-a-change-of-tactics-if-it-fails/00000191-521f-dc13-ab99-db1f4aa10000</link><description>拜登政府可能会向以色列和哈马斯提出一个不可谈判的、是或否的主张。如果内塔尼亚胡拒绝，华盛顿可能会将失败归咎于他，并可能对其政府内的极右翼采取进一步行动</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 03:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/u-s-steps-up-the-pressure-ahead-of-gaza-summit-and-plans-a-change-of-tactics-if-it-fails/00000191-521f-dc13-ab99-db1f4aa10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列代表团在重新停火、人质协议谈判之前抵达多哈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article-live/senior-palestinian-official-israeli-comments-suggest-doha-talks-unlikely-to-end-in-deal/00000191-53ce-d6a2-a7dd-d3dea0fb0000</link><description>由于火箭爆炸，上加利利发生火灾；消防队在现场执行任务 ■ 白宫柯比：信息告诉我们，伊朗尚未放弃攻击以色列的威胁 ■ 内塔尼亚胡在卡塔尔峰会前与人质协议谈判小组会面 ■ 五名巴勒斯坦人在以色列突袭和约旦河西岸袭击中丧生；四名士兵在行动中被爆炸装置炸伤 ■ 美国驻贝鲁特特使表示以色列与真主党的升级是可以避免的</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 02:26:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article-live/senior-palestinian-official-israeli-comments-suggest-doha-talks-unlikely-to-end-in-deal/00000191-53ce-d6a2-a7dd-d3dea0fb0000</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚大学校长因加沙抗议政策和反犹太主义批评而辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/columbia-university-president-resigns-amid-criticism-of-gaza-protests-policy-antisemitism/00000191-5377-d39d-a79f-f77f174a0000</link><description>米努什·沙菲克 (Minouche Shafik) 的领导层面临严格审查，鉴于她对抗议活动处理不当以及校园反犹太主义的指控，要求她辞职的呼声越来越高</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 00:58:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/columbia-university-president-resigns-amid-criticism-of-gaza-protests-policy-antisemitism/00000191-5377-d39d-a79f-f77f174a0000</guid></item><item><title>如果从以色列国防部长到伊朗的所有人都希望加沙停火，这并不是投降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-14/ty-article/.highlight/its-not-capitulation-if-everyone-from-iran-to-israels-defense-chiefs-wants-a-cease-fire/00000191-51ab-ddb5-affd-5bffb82a0000</link><description>本周，以色列国防部长、以色列公众、美国、英国和德国大使以及伊朗政府似乎达成了罕见的共识</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 17:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-14/ty-article/.highlight/its-not-capitulation-if-everyone-from-iran-to-israels-defense-chiefs-wants-a-cease-fire/00000191-51ab-ddb5-affd-5bffb82a0000</guid></item><item><title>为了避免对隔离公共祈祷的强烈反对，特拉维夫没有让任何人满意</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-bid-to-avoid-backlash-over-segregated-public-prayer-tel-aviv-leaves-no-one-satisfied/00000191-5042-d94f-adf1-d06e22ac0000</link><description>去年特拉维夫反对使用公共空间进行性别隔离祈祷的抗议活动引发了全国性的辩论，之后该市对这种做法进行了取缔。但围绕以色列世俗首都性质的争论仍在上演，一些人警告“这将以另一场爆炸告终”</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 17:00:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-bid-to-avoid-backlash-over-segregated-public-prayer-tel-aviv-leaves-no-one-satisfied/00000191-5042-d94f-adf1-d06e22ac0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔阻止阿拉伯军官指挥希伯伦边境警察，转而推挤犹太军官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-blocks-arab-officers-posting-to-command-border-police-in-hebron/00000191-518b-da93-add3-db8bcf6a0000</link><description>以色列国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔试图任命一名极端正统犹太教军官，而不是一名阿拉伯基督教军官，来指挥包括闪点族长墓在内的地区，该部长经常在那里祈祷</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 16:57:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-blocks-arab-officers-posting-to-command-border-police-in-hebron/00000191-518b-da93-add3-db8bcf6a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 313 天：以色列高级拉比谴责本格维尔访问圣殿山</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-313-senior-israeli-rabbis-condemn-ben-gvirs-temple-mount-visit/00000191-51a7-d211-a7fd-fbe7344b0001</link><description>美国总统拜登的中东事务高级特使在贝鲁特会见黎巴嫩议会议长后表示，“我们仍然相信，没有人真正希望黎巴嫩和以色列之间爆发全面战争” ■ 美国、英国和德国驻以色列特使公开呼吁立即接受加沙停火/人质释放协议 ■ 战争开始 313 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 16:14:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-313-senior-israeli-rabbis-condemn-ben-gvirs-temple-mount-visit/00000191-51a7-d211-a7fd-fbe7344b0001</guid></item><item><title>数据显示：加沙战争是 21 世纪最血腥的战争之一</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-death-toll-in-gaza-is-bad-even-compared-to-the-wars-in-ukraine-iraq-and-myanmar/00000191-50c6-d6a2-a7dd-d1decf340000</link><description>随着加沙死亡人数接近 40,000 人，国土报从全球角度审视这些数据。死亡的速度和速度，以及幸存者的生活条件，给伊拉克、乌克兰和缅甸的冲突蒙上阴影</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 16:02:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-death-toll-in-gaza-is-bad-even-compared-to-the-wars-in-ukraine-iraq-and-myanmar/00000191-50c6-d6a2-a7dd-d1decf340000</guid></item><item><title>以色列推进西岸新定居点建设</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/israel-advances-building-of-new-west-bank-settlement/00000191-50e4-d3e5-a9bd-d8e69bd60000</link><description>在一些巴勒斯坦国家单方面承认之后，以色列指定了新的土地用于定居点建设。以色列极右翼财政部长在国际谴责此举后表示，“任何反以色列或反犹太复国主义的决定都不会阻止定居点的发展”</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 14:13:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/israel-advances-building-of-new-west-bank-settlement/00000191-50e4-d3e5-a9bd-d8e69bd60000</guid></item><item><title>尽管受到伊朗和真主党的威胁，以色列北部人在经历了 10 个月的战争后返回家园</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/the-israelis-returning-north-after-10-months-of-war-despite-iran-and-hezbollah-threat/00000191-50dc-d825-a79f-dbff965d0000</link><description>“以色列混乱政府及其犯罪团伙的行为更让我担心”：在加沙战争和与真主党的冲突中流离失所数月之后，一些以色列北部人正在返回他们被遗弃的家园</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 14:08:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/the-israelis-returning-north-after-10-months-of-war-despite-iran-and-hezbollah-threat/00000191-50dc-d825-a79f-dbff965d0000</guid></item><item><title>关于以色列信用评级下调，内塔尼亚胡既对又错</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/war-is-hell-and-it-doesnt-come-cheap/00000191-50dd-dc13-ab99-dbdd1e7b0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡和财政部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇对惠誉的举动不屑一顾，称在战争期间预计会下调评级。但接下来发生的事情既掌握在伊朗和真主党手中，也掌握在以色列手中</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 12:43:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/war-is-hell-and-it-doesnt-come-cheap/00000191-50dd-dc13-ab99-dbdd1e7b0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登和哈梅内伊正在酝酿一项协议。以色列错过了早期迹象</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/biden-and-khamenei-are-cooking-up-a-deal-israel-missed-the-early-signs/00000191-5080-d387-a7d7-f08e2fbf0000</link><description>未来的调查委员会将不得不调查以色列是如何忽视伊朗的政策变化的。 ■ 与此同时，拜登也发现了一个机会。 ■ 内塔尼亚胡呢？他宁愿按时上场，但仍然可以从交易中获益</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 12:27:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/biden-and-khamenei-are-cooking-up-a-deal-israel-missed-the-early-signs/00000191-5080-d387-a7d7-f08e2fbf0000</guid></item><item><title>摩萨德前高级特工起诉以色列，指控他在审讯期间遭受酷刑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/former-top-mossad-operative-sues-israel-for-alleged-torture-during-interrogations/00000191-4713-db9a-a197-d7f71ff40000</link><description>在长达 15 年的禁言令之后，针对以色列 Shin Bet 服务的案件因《国土报》的请愿而曝光。安全机构指控前摩萨德人员参与针对以色列的间谍活动</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 10:47:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/former-top-mossad-operative-sues-israel-for-alleged-torture-during-interrogations/00000191-4713-db9a-a197-d7f71ff40000</guid></item><item><title>反对派在本格维尔议会抵制中击败了内塔尼亚胡政府的立法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/opposition-defeats-netanyahu-govt-legislation-amid-ben-gvir-knesset-boycott/00000191-504d-d94f-adf1-d06f14450000</link><description>反对党领袖亚伊尔·拉皮德 (Yair Lapid) 表示，“如果你想知道政府是如何垮台的，那就像这样”；本-格维尔的政党抵制因其加入战时内阁的要求而进行的投票，迫使政府撤回当天议程上的所有法案</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 10:42:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/opposition-defeats-netanyahu-govt-legislation-amid-ben-gvir-knesset-boycott/00000191-504d-d94f-adf1-d06f14450000</guid></item></channel></rss>